These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, trike
1. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | van | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lemon
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, scooter
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the roller is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apple | lemon      |
| Pet    | roller  | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
