.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-20::.
City: liverpool, new-york
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person traveling to new-york##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |
| Pet     | new-york | liverpool      |
| Sport   | climbing | baseball |

 